h2. 8. Data Model

h3. Aurora PostgreSQL

|| Table || Columns ||
| *test_cases* | id, env, service, title, description, scenario, steps (JSON), plan_steps (JSON), tags, created_by, created_at, team, last_result, last_run_at, embedding vector(1024), promoted_to (TEXT[]), promoted_from_id, promoted_from_env, promoted_by, promoted_at |
| *run_records* | id, test_case_id, env, result (PASS/FAIL), summary, run_by, run_at, team |

h3. DynamoDB

|| Pattern || pk || sk || Example ||
| Service config | SERVICE#\{team\}#\{env\} | \{service\}#\{key\} | pk=SERVICE#teama#dev, sk=bestbuy#BESTBUY_USA_URL |
| Test accounts | ACCOUNT#\{env\} | \{account_id\} | pk=ACCOUNT#dev, sk=qa-user-1 |
